Youwarou Cercle  is an administrative subdivision of the Mopti Region of Mali. The administrative center (chef-lieu) is the town of Youwarou.
The cercle is divided into seven communes:
*Bimbéré Tama
*Déboye
*Dirma
*Dongo
*Farimaké
*N'Dodjiga
*Youwarou
